FuncDef:
The enable command enables the IOAM function.
The undo enable command disables the IOAM function. The enable command enables the IOAM function. The undo enable command disables the IOAM function. By default, the IOAM function is disabled. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
